snippet.title: Cozy Dungeons - Trailer
snippet.description:
Cozy Dungeons
"Cozy Dungeons" is an adventure/interior design game where you explore dungeons, clear them out of enemies and renovate them for a profit. It's a unique mix of genres in the market, offering the thrills of games like "The Legend of Zelda" with the renovation seen in games like "Animal Crossing" or "House Flipper"
